From a support case 
{quote}
I defined my own personal filter in the issue navigator. In the filter I changed the visible columns and the sort order. This works fine. When I choose 'Views - Printable' the filter will be shown as I expected.

When I show the saved filter and first change the sort order (without saving it to the filter) and then choose 'Views - Printable' the filter will show more columns (in my case). If I save the filter before choosing 'Views - Printable' the printable view will show the expected number of columns and in the right sort order.
{quote}

