My team is currently working on an interface between a Lotus Notes application and JIRA. The Notes application will create remote JIRA tickets, and we'd like to know if there's a way to retrieve the list of options for selectable fields (Select List, Multi Select and Components) through the RPC API. I've been browsing through the Atlassian forums and the web, but haven't had luck with finding any info so far.

Any input will be greatly appreciated. I set the Priority to 'Critical' because we really need to sort this out in order to successfully implement our interface.

Thanks in advance!!!

